title: Pork Sausage & Roast Tomato Salsa Hot Dogs with Cheddar, Red Cabbage Salad & Garlic Aioli
description: There’s nothing quite like a hot dog to ring in summer. Golden pork sausages, hot from the oven, sit comfortably in toasted
brioche buns with a red cabbage and sweetcorn salad. A drizzle of garlic aioli and roast tomato salsa ties it all together, making
these hot dogs a mouthwatering fusion of tangy, savoury and creamy goodness.
